                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> The way taunt works is if the person who pressed the taunt button is successful (taunt is either a success or a failure, sort of like item combines or I guess the resistance rate of trying to land spells on a mob) it places the taunter 1 hate point above the highest person.  There's other things involved in agro like pathing, sitting, etc but that's the general explanation on how the taunt button works.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
