                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Taunt = (Hate_of_highest_person + 1) + (Hate_bonus)<br /><br />Hate_of_highest_person is simply that, be it a Cleric who just CHed or a Shaman who just slowed.<br />Hate_bonus is where things get tricky. This is a combination of factors like: tank's and other's proximity to MoB, whether or not mob is Rooted (which fubars aggro anyway) or Snared, etc.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
                    </tr>
